configuration.name: Device ${eui}
configuration.customFunction: function decodePayload(input) {var output = {attributes: {},telemetry: []};// --- Decoding code --- //var decoded = {};for (var i = 0; i < input.length;) {var type = input[i++] & 0xff;if (type == 0x01) { // Temperature Converts to Â°Cdecoded.temperature = parseBytesToInt(input, i, 2, true) / 10;i += 2;} else if (type == 0x02) { //Humiditydecoded.humidity = input[i];i += 1;} else if (type == 0x04) { // Lightdecoded.light = parseBytesToInt(input, i, 2, true);i += 2;} else if (type == 0x05) { // Motion (PIR)decoded.pir = input[i];i += 1;} else if (type == 0x07) { // Battery Voltage (VDD)decoded.vdd = parseBytesToInt(input, i, 2, true);   i += 2;}}output.telemetry = [{ts: timestamp,values: decoded}];// --- Decoding code --- //return output;}
